01:15:37.015 --> 01:15:43.277
They are Moshe, Daud, Elia, and Yada,

01:15:44.617 --> 01:15:45.658
even in the proper order.

01:15:47.778 --> 01:15:50.019
Although at this time they were known as

01:15:50.038 --> 01:15:54.899
the Pishown, the Giychown, the Chideqel,

01:15:55.220 --> 01:15:56.541
and the Perath.

01:15:59.198 --> 01:16:02.840
Their story is depicted in Bare’syth,

01:16:03.579 --> 01:16:06.421
two ten through two fourteen.

01:16:08.462 --> 01:16:10.943
Now, if I may.

01:16:10.962 --> 01:16:14.444
The Pishown is from Pasha with the own

01:16:14.484 --> 01:16:17.886
suffix and addresses the entirety of the

01:16:17.926 --> 01:16:20.327
rebellious nature of the Israelites

01:16:20.386 --> 01:16:21.847
encircling Moshe.

01:16:23.484 --> 01:16:23.863
Of them,

01:16:23.923 --> 01:16:26.865
Yahowah said that they are sabab.

01:16:27.286 --> 01:16:29.987
They went round and round,

01:16:30.287 --> 01:16:34.208
turning every which way while achuliyah,

01:16:34.970 --> 01:16:36.649
anguished and in travail.

01:16:37.970 --> 01:16:38.990
Hmm,

01:16:39.030 --> 01:16:41.372
certainly describes Moshe's experience

01:16:41.993 --> 01:16:45.394
during the Exodus, doesn't it?

01:16:45.413 --> 01:16:48.796
Giychown is all things pertaining to Gish,

01:16:49.155 --> 01:16:50.216
being brought forth.

01:16:51.024 --> 01:16:54.247
Bursting onto the scene, it depicts Dowd,

01:16:54.846 --> 01:16:56.569
a son who is given to us,

01:16:57.128 --> 01:16:59.310
whose three lives would change the world.

01:16:59.730 --> 01:17:01.171
He burst onto the scene as an

01:17:01.231 --> 01:17:01.993
eight-year-old.

01:17:02.953 --> 01:17:05.355
He burst back onto the scene to fulfill

01:17:05.435 --> 01:17:06.195
Pesach, Matzah,

01:17:06.216 --> 01:17:08.878
and Bikuwrym exactly as he said he would

01:17:09.418 --> 01:17:11.100
in your four thousand year,

01:17:11.119 --> 01:17:11.940
thirty-three CE.

01:17:12.001 --> 01:17:15.684
He'll burst out of the sky and onto

01:17:15.904 --> 01:17:17.685
Jerusalem, the city of Dowd.

01:17:18.811 --> 01:17:20.113
In twenty-thirty-three,

01:17:20.132 --> 01:17:21.372
you're six thousand, yeah?

01:17:24.675 --> 01:17:26.475
He's the one that burst out of Sheol

01:17:28.136 --> 01:17:30.398
to become the living embodiment of Bokor,

01:17:31.559 --> 01:17:33.300
firstborn children in Boko Haram.

01:17:36.240 --> 01:17:39.882
The Chidekel is from Chidek.

01:17:41.057 --> 01:17:44.399
revealing that Hoya would be a thorn in

01:17:44.418 --> 01:17:46.979
the sides of the religious and political,

01:17:47.500 --> 01:17:51.201
serving as a sarcastic prick to pierce

01:17:51.921 --> 01:17:53.521
through their nasty facade.

01:17:53.542 --> 01:17:59.144
Now, prick means to be like a thorn.

01:18:00.363 --> 01:18:01.845
One in the foot, one in the hand,

01:18:01.944 --> 01:18:03.625
one in the arm, one in the side.

01:18:04.246 --> 01:18:04.645
As such,

01:18:04.685 --> 01:18:06.426
he is shown as the thorn in the

01:18:06.506 --> 01:18:08.127
side of Asher.

01:18:10.315 --> 01:18:11.576
the mother goddess cults,

01:18:12.877 --> 01:18:14.197
mother goddess of Assyria,

01:18:14.216 --> 01:18:17.677
the other goddesses who were so prevalent

01:18:18.417 --> 01:18:21.378
in their similar religiosity to the mother

01:18:21.439 --> 01:18:22.918
goddess cult in Israel.

01:18:24.220 --> 01:18:24.739
Oh, and by the way,

01:18:24.779 --> 01:18:27.100
Asher is also the whore of Babylon who

01:18:27.240 --> 01:18:28.820
Elia will prick as well,

01:18:30.341 --> 01:18:32.042
piercing through her nasty facade.

01:18:35.707 --> 01:18:36.787
Ah, the Parath.

01:18:37.488 --> 01:18:39.309
Well, it's the Euphrates, and as such,

01:18:39.729 --> 01:18:41.550
it is the river that drains the swamp

01:18:41.590 --> 01:18:42.131
of Babel.

01:18:43.131 --> 01:18:45.332
Confusing commingling of religion and

01:18:45.372 --> 01:18:45.912
politics.

01:18:46.511 --> 01:18:49.194
And it is from here that Judaism's Talmud

01:18:49.873 --> 01:18:52.875
was conceived and that Islam was derived.

01:18:53.916 --> 01:18:55.895
I know a guy that spoke of those

01:18:55.935 --> 01:18:58.016
things, draining those swamps.

01:18:59.417 --> 01:19:02.038
It is, of course, from Parath.

01:19:03.755 --> 01:19:04.295
Therefore,

01:19:04.815 --> 01:19:06.997
it addresses the productive and fruitful

01:19:07.037 --> 01:19:11.819
bull, the Adamah Parah.

01:19:11.838 --> 01:19:14.779
Yada.

01:19:15.100 --> 01:19:17.081
God doesn't miss an opportunity to paint

01:19:17.121 --> 01:19:18.442
portraits with words.

01:19:19.542 --> 01:19:21.703
So we should expect no less going forward.

01:19:23.564 --> 01:19:25.185
And I think this is the proper time

01:19:25.204 --> 01:19:26.126
